00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:22,400
¡No fui yo!

283
00:16:22,400 --> 00:16:23,200
¡Soy inocente!

284
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,680
¡Perdóname!

285
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:25,720
¡Te lo suplico, por favor!

286
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,520
¡No quiero morir!

287
00:16:28,147 --> 00:16:30,080
(Chenda Capital)

288
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:37,480
