289
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:39,040
Ella...

290
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:42,200
Wange presentó su renuncia.

291
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,680
Señor Song.

292
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,320
Zhang Wange.

293
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:56,920
Zhang Wange.

294
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,320
¡Abre la puerta!

295
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,080
Sé que estás adentro.

296
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,960
Hablemos.

297
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,600
Señor Song.

298
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,080
Ya renuncié.

299
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,200
Pero no lo aprobé.

300
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,520
Por lo tanto, la renuncia no es válida.

301
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:42,880
¿Qué quieres?

302
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,240
Sobre lo de anoche,

303
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,600
Lo siento.

304
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:57,040
No pasó nada entre nosotros anoche.

305
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,800
Iré a trabajar.

306
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:03,600
Tengo mucha curiosidad

307
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,040
sobre tu propósito

308
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,240
al venir a Chenda.

309
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:12,000
Sea lo que sea,

310
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,240
simplemente nos estamos

311
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,800
usando mutuamente para obtener lo que necesitamos.

312
00:18:16,032 --> 00:18:18,040
(Así que ella lo sabía todo el tiempo.)

313
00:18:23,303 --> 00:18:28,238
